direchanged is used to determine if the contents of a directory has changed.

use the --gen parameter to generate the hash used in checking:

$ dirchanged --gen test
e3b0c44298fc1c149afbf4c8996fb92427ae41e4649b934ca495991b7852b855

use the --check parameter to monitor the directory:

$ dirchanged --check test e3b0c44298fc1c149afbf4c8996fb92427ae41e4649b934ca495991b7852b855
dirchanged OK - directory has not changed: test
